## Documentation Patterns

### API Documentation
```markdown
## `functionName(param1, param2)`

Brief description.

### Parameters

| Name | Type | Required | Description |
|------|------|----------|-------------|
| `param1` | `string` | Yes | What it does |
| `param2` | `number` | No | Default: `10` |

### Returns

`Promise<ResultType>` - Description of return value.

### Throws

- `ValidationError` - When input is invalid
- `NetworkError` - When request fails

### Example

```typescript
const result = await functionName('value', 42)
```
```

