## Best Practices

### Do
- Start with a clear project description
- Include installation instructions
- Provide usage examples
- Document all public APIs
- Keep README concise, link to detailed docs
- Use consistent formatting
- Include badges for quick info

### Don't
- Write walls of text
- Assume reader knows everything
- Skip examples
- Let documentation get outdated
- Include sensitive information
- Over-document internal APIs
